### 1. Login owner
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "andrey@example.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 2. Create company
POST http://localhost:3000/api/companies
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_OWNER_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "StayFlow Marbella",
  "plan": "FREE"
}

### 3. Get my company
GET http://localhost:3000/api/companies/me
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_OWNER_TOKEN

### 4. Invite manager
POST http://localhost:3000/api/team/invite
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_OWNER_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Manager One",
  "email": "manager@stayflow.app",
  "phone": "+34000000001",
  "role": "MANAGER",
  "temporaryPassword": "123456"
}

### 5. Invite worker
POST http://localhost:3000/api/team/invite
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_OWNER_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Worker One",
  "email": "worker@stayflow.app",
  "phone": "+34000000002",
  "role": "WORKER",
  "temporaryPassword": "123456"
}

### 6. List team
GET http://localhost:3000/api/team
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_OWNER_TOKEN
